B&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">，白天相对温暖，夜晚较凉，容易有夜雨，四月以后，春暖花开；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">夏天的</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">，白天较热，晚上微凉，但因为是雨季，所以容易有雨；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">秋季的</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">，白天温暖，晚上较凉，属于一年四季中最美的时候。</span><br/><img src=\"http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/8A/15/wKgBs1g9KeWAX94GAApdxVrQmJA02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F700%2Fq%2F90%7Cwatermark%2F1%2Fimage%2FaHR0cDovL24xLXEubWFmZW5nd28ubmV0L3MxMS9NMDAvOTEvNzAvd0tnQkVGcF9faTZBUHYtZEFBQUwxMzg3aE0wNjk5LnBuZw%3D%3D%2Fgravity%2FSouthEast%2Fdx%2F10%2Fdy%2F11\" class=\"_js_answerPic _j_show_original\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 700px; cursor: pointer; margin: 8px 0px 25px; display: block; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal; height: auto; width: 700px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220);\"/><br/><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">二、玩几天合适？</strong><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">这个问题取决于你有多少时间，想怎么玩了。</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">不过，有两个基本规律可以遵循：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">1、因为初到</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">，一般人都会出现程度不同的高原反应。所以建议在</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">至少先玩2天，这也是给身体一个适应高原环境的过程。而且</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">是西藏医疗条件最好的地区，如果出现严重高原反应，救治非常方便，即使立即返回内地，飞机、火车也是最发达的。</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">2、就算在</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">玩2－3天，也要遵循着先易后难，先轻松再剧烈的方式。即为了慢慢适应高原环境，不要初到</span></p><div class=\"area_tags _j_tip_mdd\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; display: inline-block; width: auto; z-index: 10; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\"><a class=\"at_link\" href=\"http://undefined\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\">拉萨</a></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">就剧烈运动（如爬山），而是应该先从轻松一些的项目开始，慢慢加运动量。</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">所以，在这里的建议是，至少玩2天，基本玩3天，再多加时间也可以。</span><br/><br/><strong style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">三、如何安排日程？</strong><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">我先把基本3日行程详细写给大家，然后会给一些特殊行程的计划。</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">根据各景点的远近和不同特点，一般安排如下：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">D1：罗布林卡－西藏博物馆－文成公主表演（2018年注：西藏博物馆已于2016年年底关闭重新修葺，可时开放待定）</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">第一天，以适应高原环境为主。罗布林卡为夏宫，基本都是平地，没有上下攀登等剧烈运动；西藏博物馆在罗布林卡东门马路对面，可以事先了解西藏的历史文化，对后面的游览参观做准备。这一天相当宽松，晚上可以去看文成公主表演，但由于昼夜温差大，需要换厚衣服。</span></p><p><br/></p>');
